        ns2:RequirementSpecification ;
    rdfs:comment "minimum height of 28 cm" ;
    ns2:requirementSatisfiedBy <http://example.org/req/397#Spec_2> .

<http://example.org/req/397#Req_3> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
